com.vmware.vapi.protocol.server.rpc.http.impl

Class TcServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.protocol.server.rpc.http.impl.AbstractServer
      • com.vmware.vapi.protocol.server.rpc.http.impl.TcServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LifecycleListener, LifecycleManager, Server

    public class TcServer
extends AbstractServer
    Receives requests and passes them for processing through the configured server processing steps. Once ready transmits responses back to the client. Uses tcServer with Tomcat 7.0.
